data.description: Welcome to this delightful 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom ranch home, a gem nestled on a 0.2-acre, fully fenced in, corner lot in the heart of a walkable neighborhood, mere steps from the vibrant downtown Plainfield. The inviting covered front porch sets the tone for the cozy living spaces within. Step inside to discover a living room that seamlessly opens to a dining area, where an exposed brick beam adds a touch of rustic charm. The kitchen is a heartwarming space, featuring a stylish backsplash, and practical center island with a breakfast bar - perfect for morning coffees and casual meals. Retreat to the primary bedroom, offering serenity with its private bathroom, complete with a fully tiled shower and a refreshing rainfall shower head. This home also features a detached 1-car garage with ample storage and additional space, connected by a private walkway, ensuring convenience and security. This home is perfect blend of a peaceful lifestyle with the buzz of the city within reach. Don't let this unique opportunity slip away. Schedule your showing today and take the first step towards making this charming house your new home today! Back on market at no fault of the seller.
